---
import ServicePage from '../layouts/ServicePage.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How much pain should I expect from a bikini wax?",
    answer: "Everyone has a different pain threshold, but our esthetician can reduce pain and discomfort by getting wax to the right temperature. The experienced esthetician will have mind-body techniques such as breathing suggestions and other ways to calm the pain receptors."
  },
  {
    question: "What's the difference between a bikini and Brazilian wax?",
    answer: "A bikini wax removes hair that would be visible around the bikini line. A Brazilian wax removes all or most hair from the front, back, and everything in between. With a Brazilian, you can choose to leave a small strip, triangle, or go completely bare."
  },
  {
    question: "How should I prepare for my bikini wax?",
    answer: "Make sure you have at least ¼ inch of hair growth so that the wax can properly capture the hair. You can prep your skin with a warm bath or a gentle exfoliating product the night before your appointment."
  }
];
---

<ServicePage
  title="Bikini Wax Phoenix AZ | Effective Bikini Line Hair Waxing"
  description="Get a premium bikini wax experience at Rejuvenate You in Phoenix. We offer professional pubic hair removal for fresher and smoother skin. Schedule an appointment now!"
  price="$45"
  duration="10-15 min"
  location="phoenix" currentLocation="phoenix"
  faqs={faqs}
>

<!-- Hero Image -->
<div class="mb-8">
  <img 
    src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_3e73bab7-6149-42c4-a35d-e694cc211f04_bikini-waxing-scottsdale.jpg"
    alt="Bikini wax service at Rejuvenate You in Phoenix"
    class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover rounded-xl"
  />
</div>

<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  Get a premium bikini wax experience at Rejuvenate You in Phoenix. We offer professional bikini line hair removal for fresher and smoother skin. Schedule an appointment now!
</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Benefits of a Bikini Wax</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_7bf54216-e954-4b43-9ab6-815b0706664c_benefits-of-bikini-waxing.jpg"
      alt="Benefits of bikini waxing"
      class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="mb-4">
      Pubic hair removal is more popular than ever, and bikini waxing is one of the most convenient and effective ways to achieve smooth skin.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The feeling of rejuvenation and renewal is a reason why most chose to get this service.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
      <li>Longer-lasting smoothness than shaving</li>
      <li>No razor burn or irritation</li>
      <li>Hair grows back finer over time</li>
      <li>Confidence at the beach or pool</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <p class="text-gray-700">
    With shaving, you're cutting the hair above the root. The same hair will grow back and often develop a thick and stubbly feel as it does so. This process can be very uncomfortable, and results typically don't last more than a week.
  </p>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">How Much Pain Should You Expect?</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="mb-4">
      Everyone has a different pain threshold, but our esthetician can reduce pain and discomfort by getting wax to the right temperature. It should be hot enough to melt not warm enough to hurt your skin. The experienced esthetician will have mind-body techniques such as breathing suggestions and other ways to calm the pain receptors.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      There is also an expert gesture to tear off the wax in a swift motion. If done quickly and effectively, this part of the process causes brief and minimal pain.
    </p>
    <p>
      Don't hesitate to voice your concerns regarding pain and discomfort. Our esthetician will answer all your questions and make sure you have the most comfortable experience.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_63581fe5dc4eec2e7c48d21f_waxing-service-scottsdale.jpeg"
      alt="Professional bikini waxing"
      class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
    />
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Difference Between a Bikini & Brazilian Wax</h2>

<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Bikini Wax</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Removes hair that would be visible around the bikini line. This is a great option for those who want to clean up the sides without going completely bare.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Brazilian Wax</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Removes all or most hair from the front, back, and everything in between. You can choose to leave a small strip, triangle, or go completely bare.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

