<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ol class="space-y-4">
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">1.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Consultation</strong> — We discuss your preferences and any concerns.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">2.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Preparation</strong> — The area is cleansed and prepped for waxing.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">3.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Waxing</strong> — Using quality hard wax, we remove unwanted hair efficiently.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">4.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Aftercare</strong> — Soothing products are applied and we provide care instructions.
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Schedule Your Bikini Wax in Phoenix</h2>

<p class="text-lg">
  Ready for smooth, confident skin? <a href="https://app.squareup.com/appointments/book/e9ycxyisf79aby/L96KEQZQVHJ37/start" style="color: #7B2D8E;" class="font-semibold hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Book your bikini wax appointment</a> at our Phoenix location today!
</p>

</ServicePage>
